OL,3,CSixteen arrested after nine cannabis
OL,4,Cfactories found
OL,6,FSixteen people have been arrested
OL,7,Fafter police uncovered nine cannabis
OL,8,Ffactories across Northern Ireland.
OL,10,FIt followed searches by detectives
OL,11,Ffrom the Organised Crime Branch in
OL,12,Fcounties Armagh, Tyrone and Fermanagh
OL,13,Fon Tuesday and Wednesday.
OL,15,FThey said cannabis plants with an
OL,16,Festimated street value of about #1.1
OL,17,Fmillion were seized.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/7
