OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1782325132
OL,3,CSixteen arrested after nine cannabis
OL,4,Cfactories found
OL,6,FSix were charged with a range of drug-
OL,7,Frelated offences, including
OL,8,Fcultivating cannabis, being concerned
OL,9,Fin the supply of a Class B controlled
OL,10,Fdrug, and dishonestly using
OL,11,Felectricity.
OL,13,FThe men, aged 20, 23, 34, 42, 51 and
OL,14,F53, are expected to appear before
OL,15,FStrabane Magistrates' Court on
OL,16,FThursday.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/7
