OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1782325132
OL,3,CSixteen arrested after nine cannabis
OL,4,Cfactories found
OL,6,F"Nine grow houses were located across
OL,7,Fa number of towns and villages within
OL,8,FCounties Armagh, Tyrone and Fermanagh
OL,9,F` namely Armagh, Newtownhamilton,
OL,10,FKeady, Killylea, Coalisland,
OL,11,FAughnacloy, Omagh, and Clabby," police
OL,12,Fsaid.
OL,14,F"During the searches, cannabis plants
OL,15,Fwith a collective estimated street
OL,16,Fvalue of approximately #1.1 million
OL,17,Fwere seized."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@_O]vD@AOUyD@MO]
