CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1782325132
OL,3,CSixteen arrested after nine cannabis
OL,4,Cfactories found
OL,6,FOf the 16 arrests, 14 men were
OL,7,Fdetained on suspicion of drug-related
OL,8,Foffences as part of an ongoing
OL,9,Finvestigation into suspected cannabis
OL,10,Fcultivation and associated criminality.
OL,12,FThe other two men were arrested on
OL,13,Fsuspicion of possessing counterfeit
OL,14,Fcurrency.
OL,16,FThirteen remained in custody on
OL,17,FWednesday afternoon, while two were
OL,18,Freleased on bail and one released
OL,19,Funconditionally.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
