FL,412,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1782325132
OL,3,CSixteen arrested after nine cannabis
OL,4,Cfactories found
OL,6,FThe police said most of the properties
OL,7,Fsearched were in rural locations, with
OL,8,Fmany of the structures significant in
OL,9,Fsize and sophistication, and would
OL,10,Fhave involved considerable planning,
OL,11,Finvestment and time.
OL,13,F"Illegal grow operations, of such
OL,14,Fcomplexity, are without doubt
OL,15,Fgenerating profits for criminal
OL,16,Fnetworks," they added.
OL,18,F"Organised crime groups who exploit
OL,19,Fothers, in this case through the
OL,20,Fsupply of drugs, have one aim only and
OL,21,Fthat's to line their own pockets.
OL,26,@uD@AOUxD@JO]zD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,412,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1782325132
OL,3,CSixteen arrested after nine cannabis
OL,4,Cfactories found
OL,6,F"Sadly, this often comes at the
OL,7,Fexpense of vulnerable people.
OL,9,F"The investigation is extremely
OL,10,Fsignificant in terms of the number of
OL,11,Fconstructions identified, the
OL,12,Fsubsequent number of arrests and the
OL,13,Fvolume of seizures.
OL,15,F"By identifying and shutting down the
OL,16,Fgrow houses, and by making arrests,
OL,17,Fwe're helping to stop criminality in
OL,18,Fits tracks. Our investigation will,
OL,19,Fhowever, continue beyond today's
OL,20,Farrests."
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@AOUwD@AOU
